        <item>
            <title>特朗普被枪击后振臂相片，美联社摄影师 + Sony A9III 拍摄</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/15/donaldtrump-shooting-photographer-evanvucci/dc/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=donaldtrump-shooting-photographer-evanvucci</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/15/donaldtrump-shooting-photographer-evanvucci/dc/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Ngan Ivan]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 07:40:17 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[城中热话]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[数码相机]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Donald Trump]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Evan Vucci]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[SONY]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Sony A9III]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[普立兹奖]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1250373</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">近日最轰动的新闻莫过于美国总统候选人 Donald Trump 在宾夕法尼亚州举行的政治集会上被枪击，他耳朵中弹后重新站立，脸上沾满鲜血振臂高呼的相片在网络上疯传。原来拍下这张照片的摄影师大有来头，曾经获得过普立兹新闻奖和默罗新闻奖，是来自美联社的摄影师 Evan Vucci。</p><div class="video-container"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">Republican presidential candidate former President Donald Trump raises his fist as he is rushed off stage  after an assassination attempt during a campaign rally in Butler, Pa. <a href="https://twitter.com/APNews?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@apnews</a><a href="https://t.co/VoAYqRC4QV">pic.twitter.com/VoAYqRC4QV</a></p><p>&mdash; Evan Vucci (@evanvucci) <a href="https://twitter.com/evanvucci/status/1812330828371763638?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">July 14, 2024</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div><p style="font-weight: 400;">在 Donald Trump 枪击事件发生后，Evan Vucci 拍摄的照片成为了最多人分享的照片。Evan 分享拍摄下这张照片的整个经过，他形容摄影师被安排在距离讲台大约 30 cm 的区域，Evan 原本位于讲台的左侧，案发时与一众摄影师跑到预料 Donald Trump 会离场的地方。他表示当时一直告诉自己要冷静，因为这是美国历史上其中一个最重大的时刻，必须保持头脑清醒将它记录下来。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1250385 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/1-20-694x354.jpg" alt="Sony A9III" width="694" height="354" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/1-20-694x354.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/1-20.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.sony.com.hk/zh/electronics/interchangeable-lens-cameras/ilce-9m3">Sony Hong Kong</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">Evan Vucci 当时使用的相机是 Sony 的 A9 III，其快门设计具备捕捉快速移动主体的强大性能。他冒着生命危险成功拍下照片，背景倒挂的美国国旗再加上 Donald Trump 在保镳包围之中激昂地振臂高呼，被纽约时报记者 Matina Stevis-Gridneff 在他的 X 平台上称赞这张照片是新闻摄影的顶点，为历史性突发新闻拍下了完美构图的照片。预料这张照片将会为 Evan Vucci 带来另一座普立兹奖。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">资料来源：<a href="https://www.washingtonpost.com/style/media/2024/07/14/trump-shooting-photojournalists/">The Washington Post</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">图片来源：<a href="https://x.com/evanvucci/status/1812330828371763638">Evan Vucci</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/14/sony-ult-wear-wh-ult900n/mobile-music/headphones/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【评测】Sony ULT WEAR WH-ULT900N 真无线重低音头戴耳机，两种重低音模式比较 + 性价比高 + 续航力高</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/24/sony-xperia-1-vi-review/review-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【评测】Sony Xperia 1 VI　外形　手感　屏幕　相机　功能　效能开箱评测</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/15/sony-xperia-1-vi-first-review/review-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【评测】Sony Xperia 1 VI　外形　手感　屏幕　相机　介面快速评测 + 开卖详情公布</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/15/donaldtrump-shooting-photographer-evanvucci/dc/">特朗普被枪击后振臂相片，美联社摄影师 + Sony A9III 拍摄</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
